    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>In this work we have analysed the use of two different correlation metrics and two different datasets, detecting differences in the extent and directionality of the correlation between COVID-19 infection and BCG immunization. Correlation between COVID-19 infection, death rates and BCG immunization is strongly affected by the correlation metrics and so will be their biological interpretation.</jats:p>",
